elements.name: Como usuario accedo a la plataforma Ghost, creo una publicación y la programo con una fecha invalida

steps.name: I am correctly authenticated with "<USERNAME>" and "<PASSWORD>"
I am creating a new post
I fill the title with "<TITLE_POST_INVALID>" and the content with "<CONTENT_POST_INVALID>"
I want to schedule the post
I select the option to schedule for later
I enter "<POST_DATE_INVALID>" and "<POST_TIME_INVALID>" as publication date
I press the button to finish configurating the post
I should get a message error for invalid date
